===Etymology===
Germanic ''*fulmō'', from Indo-European ''*palam-, plām-''.  Cognate with Old High German ''[[folma]]''; and (''from Indo-European'') with Latin ''[[palma]]'', Old Irish ''[[lám]]'' (Welsh ''[[llaw]]'').

